<br>
Necros are easy. Their pet is out of the game (Panic the dead, spook the dead, and they dont have immune to fear like mages), his dots work too slow, and he usually cant lifetap or channel good enough to make up for my pounding on him. However, with Harm Shield, they can escape you quite often and zone, zone back etc.<br>
<br>
