and I have my poison skill 2 points from max on make and maxed on apply, My poison is basically unresistable to PC's(Ive tested myself on someone with DMF, shadoo, and PR gear his PR was in the 200+ range just for this purpose).<br>
SK's kill necro's very easy (I also have a 31 SK on rallos).<br>
well not kill  maybe (harm shield) but win . especially 57+ when the HT does over 75% of the necro's health. lifetaps are also unresistable in PvP , at least i have never seen them resisted . This is the only class I can't beat, I would *really* like to change that <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/upoisindaggerfist.showPublicProfile?language=EN>PoisinDaggerfist</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(6/12/01 12:42:19 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: SK &gt; me .... bad</span><hr size=1> Put on your AC/hp gear and grab a golem wand and a blind/root poison.  Mash your disarm and ID keys.<br>
